Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The season when cherry blossoms fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In a town with a long history, standing at the botton of a hill.\NWhere people go for education up and including university.\NPrivate school Seiohkan academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soft rays of sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the colors of the wind are warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they gently envelop everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Private school Seiohkan academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Cute scool uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Liberal scool philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A campus with greenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On such a spring day, the two meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, they would realize that\Nit was a meeting of first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"First Love." To fall in love for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Minoru Hatsushima (Age 20) attends this campus\Nalong with his good friends,\Nand they're enjoying their\Ncarefree school life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they didn't realize it at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was a memory to be treasured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Minoru Hatsushima (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might not have known it before,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Anzu Hatsushima (Age 20)    Youko Nishimura (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in that instant, they felt those feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Miki Katou (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings of "that person is precious."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Tatsuya Futaki (Age 20)   Naoya Kamata (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those will then become unforgettable feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Komomo Sakurai (Age 21)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The season when cherry blossoms fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would come to know that\Nit was a meeting of first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a story of such a spring day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Episode 1: Confession\N"I like you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta cheer for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I {\i1}have{\i0} to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu! Don't wander away from the cheering!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youko-chan, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother isn't cheering for Komomo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that true, Hatsushima?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just why did {\i1}I{\i0} have to come here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's your senpai and all, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you {\i1}do{\i0} get to see\NYouko-chan in cheerleader gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing the same thing I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, she's just Sakurai-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any reason to cheer for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Senpai's wearing a mini-skirt, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why'd you try to bring a guy along\Nwith such dirty tactics?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's about to hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who I am, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's because I smashed the ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then it hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better keep the area cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, that won't cool him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right, Youko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, if only your face hadn't been in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai lost the match because\Nshe was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? You lost, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why are you apologizing, Minoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} should be apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for hitting you with the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't worry, I don't think\Nthis'll be too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Minoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I sense a good mood between\NBig Brother and Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Some things you just don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oww! I didn't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did Komomo-senpai act\Nlike she knew you back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just crazy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, not {\i1}crazy talk{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She totally knew you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Komomo-senpai's an old friend of mine,\Njust like Youko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd want to talk about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do we have to talk about {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's interesting, {\i1}duh{\i\0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noo~! I hate noogies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let up on the crazy talk when we're\Naround other people, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-pon told me something interesting\Nabout your friend Kamata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, you'll {\i1}want{\i0} to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?{здесь я отчётливо слышу "Каната", а Анзу вроде бы говорит "Камата".}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, he and Miki-chan started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's so interesting about that, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Miki-pon and Kamata-kun\Nare having a party tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making fun of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for Miki-chan\Nand Kamata. Bigtime.{а здесь "Камата", видимо синонимы.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-pon was all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something weird\Nabout all of Anzu's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cheers! - Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, why don't we have a few words\Nfrom today's main attraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a girlfriend; good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamata, you gotta stand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. I, Naoya Kamata,\Nand Miki Katou to my left
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do here declare in everyone's presence\Nthat since last weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have been officially involved\Nin a romantic relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please treat us well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, you lucky punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a girlfriend for the first time\Nis a once-in-a-lifetime cleared event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that comes along naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His confidence is astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question! Be honest, how was this decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, as fellow members of the\NMaiden Society, we have a right to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, tell us {\i1}everything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, it'll be easy, just get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,онто нэ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he confessed to me, I said "okay"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}too{\i0} easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made the decision to date him just from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you receive a confession yourself,\Nyou'll understand, Youko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-pon is {\i1}sooo{\i0} in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous... I want a girlfriend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Minoru?\NEven {\i1}you{\i0} want a girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the place where you got hit yesterday still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that place? It's\Njust fine, never been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Minoru! Did something happen\Nbetween you and Sakurai-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, just a little incident... yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this: I hit him with a tennis ball yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tennis ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to peep at Sakurai-senpai\Nin her tennis outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You undressed her with your eyes, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no, it wasn't like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went with us to cheer at Senpai's\Npractice match yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you invite me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to look out for your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, I got dragged along by Anzu,\NI had no choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-chan, drag me along next time too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the social parasite, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it really bugs me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really were "struck" by Senpai too, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, Nishimura!\NBe careful what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It seems like\NSenpai doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worry about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whether it's all right to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's Miki-chan and... who was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kamata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could they be up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Minoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone, aren't we, Naoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know when someone might come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't do anything weird, I won't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't get enough of your cute voice, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who ever called Miki cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be discovered if we take our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Then the fun starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki, you look so embarrassed... but\NI like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoya-kun... don't spread me too much now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you have a shy side... especially right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I get started now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoya-kun, we're short on time today,\Nso we'll have to make this a quickie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Miki will be on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it slow... it still hurts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've passed that stage, Naoya-kun...\Nhaving sex feels good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We saw everything... what if they find out... oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Senpai, if we stick around, they'll know we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being such a voyeur, Miki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakurai-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does what we saw bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it {\i1}doesn't{\i0} bother me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if those two are bound\Nby the red string of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wonder if something like that\Nexists for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well... I would think it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause you're so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and our little peepshow back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our secret, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't think Miki-chan would\Nget mad, but she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pinky promise, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't head back,\Nthey might worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things may have gone well for you yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't let you get a single step ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Komomo-senpai\Ndisappeared yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did anything happen, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened. Noth-ing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Anzu, there's no way\Nyour brother has that kind of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I turn my losing streak around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate losing so much, what're\Nyou gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be requesting relations with\NSakurai-senpai, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heading for disaster with that approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're really going to ask her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the only thing I can do is try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing Kamata yesterday,\NI'm really jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's hopeless, I have to make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... I know it's\Nimpudent of me to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking,\N"If Senpai doesn't have a significant other..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...maybe I would be good enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... if you say you don't want to,\NI won't hold it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Futaki-kun...\NI'm sorry, I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... like I said...\NI can accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you don't need\Nto worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... should just leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you spying on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was just getting something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd be\N{\i1}confessing{\i0} to her back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...\Nyou saw me getting rejected, too??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be looking for a new target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave the aftermath to you, Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "aftermath"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go in there and succeed where I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give itryour best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean\Nto spy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the wrong place\Nat the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment for eavesdropping,\Ncome with me for a chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Futaki-kun went and said\Nhe liked me, I turned him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Futaki-kun is your friend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tatsuya's the kind of guy who\Ndoesn't regret trying things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't think badly of you at all, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's pretty unlikely, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun, you're not looking\Nat me when you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you turn Tatsuya down, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's smart, a bit of a flake,\Nbut he's cool enough overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just why was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your heart skip a beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you... just testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just a bit. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your heart did skip a beat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minoru-kun,\Nhow would you react?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you react if I said I liked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I shouldn't... you don't want to\Nhear that from girl you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh... "I like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? Umm, Minoru-kun, it skipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart skipped {\i1}several{\i0} beats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun, I do wonder if you like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was a test, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind if it were true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, awhile ago we saw something amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you smell anything strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Smell"? Smell what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, when we were watching\NMiki-chan and Kamata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... smell strange to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help noticing it afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, my attention was on\Nother things, so I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I just revealed something\Nembarrassing when I didn't even have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must think I'm a naughty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be so disappointed...\Nand disillusioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm much naughtier than\NI look... are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:17:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you give the "okay"\Nwhen I said I liked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you...\Nare you okay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Though I am unworthy, please take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, did I make you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I waited for about fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I got here fifteen minutes early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I liked watching you rushing to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it really gave it that "first date" feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, Minoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I ran around a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get something to drink, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun's so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went that way, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Huh? What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should head back, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun... I'm sorry! I got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hatsushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Minoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now? I'm next to a park info map.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A park info map?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the Ferris wheel from where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think it's to my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'll go look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I won't. I'm sorry, Minoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hang up the phone; my heart\Ncan't take it, Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of recognize this area. I should be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just passed the Ferris wheel, so it should\Nbe straight ahead from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know my phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called Anzu as a last resort,\Nand she gave me the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your phone is red too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Anzu said this one was too hard to use,\Nso she forced me to trade phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out, my phone is also red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe we're joined by the red phones\Nof fate, rather than the red string.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about today; it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally had our first date, and I\Nwould've been sad if I'd ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a bit of a shock, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You {\i1}are{\i0} holding it against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No two ways about it,\Nit certainly was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll do something to raise your\Nspirits, so that you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gradually catching up to Miki-chan\Nand Kamata, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, catching up to those two would involve...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you already know I'm a horny older girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than "too early",\NI'd say we're not ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not quite ready either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if anyone can see us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried because we\Nspied on Kamata and Miki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can never be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt good, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down, Minoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm older,\NI'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so big, Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so glad. Somehow,\Nthis makes me feel good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun, that was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\NI got it on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that,\Nit's your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}this{\i0} is what you meant by your "scent".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun, can you smell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.17,0:24:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it must be so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.88,0:25:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going, Minoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.55,0:25:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.98,0:25:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.16,0:25:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When I was able to say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.83,0:25:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}it was the beginning of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.78,0:26:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even when we pass each other by
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.78,0:26:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't want anyone to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.00,0:26:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}With all the voice I have
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.24,0:25:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a little fast, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.37,0:25:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little {\i1}too{\i0} fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.87,0:25:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-chan and Kamata will be surprised for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.92,0:25:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can start dating\Nwithout debate or hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.34,0:25:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.26,0:25:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-kun, are you okay with sharing lots\Nof embarrassing and exciting experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.68,0:26:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as happy and sad experiences, with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.31,0:26:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.48,0:26:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.14,0:26:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Lots and lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.44,0:26:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kiss me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.82,0:26:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please let us be lovers from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.29,0:26:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I trick you with a "Good Morning".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.21,0:26:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I feel like sighing over
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.13,0:26:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}these lonely, unspeakable, tangible emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.18,0:26:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Underneath this uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.98,0:26:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}my heart is lost in its first feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.73,0:26:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When I realize you're always on my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.78,0:27:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}that's when I know it's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.70,0:27:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lying awake in my bed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.46,0:27:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the words I want to say keep\Nfloating back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.88,0:27:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Will I be able to say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.38,0:27:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}as if it were just a greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.47,0:27:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gazing from far away
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.02,0:27:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to stop, change, and shout out
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.98,0:27:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}these emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.45,0:27:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My heart beats under this uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.33,0:27:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I can't control it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.91,0:27:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When my small body feels this powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:28:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}that's when I know it's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.41,0:28:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I can't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.16,0:28:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please, God,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.67,0:28:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}won't you make me brave?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.46,0:28:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Underneath this uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.26,0:28:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}my heart longs to express its first feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.14,0:28:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You stood there with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.06,0:28:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}as you waved your hand goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.94,0:29:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}to my old weak crybaby self.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.95,0:29:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two who had expressed their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.78,0:29:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the moment they realized their love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.71,0:29:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus followed a miraculous occurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.50,0:30:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their feelings were pure,\Ngrand, and also clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.88,0:30:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore they sometimes disagree\Nand misunderstand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.60,0:30:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their bond was\Na thing of certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.81,0:30:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grasp it strongly and never let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.06,0:30:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on First Love: Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.11,0:30:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were precious memories\Nof a precious girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.24,0:30:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a precious promise.